# Slice Agent Workflow

- Detect module boundaries from manifests, directory structure, and key files.
- Convert each significant slice into a markdown mini-agent with a clear path and task scope.
- Keep the flagship model focused on orchestration while mini-agents hold local task context.
- Escalate only when a task crosses slice boundaries or changes shared contracts.
